{"tid":437041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醉漢大鬧北⻆　木方插貨車玻璃","createTime":"2017-10-15T15:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T15:36:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"75a65ab72d43034e1c94f5df69279563ffbb5973","tid":437041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:32:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171015/20183456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171015%2F20183456&d=8rPCp%2BJ5%2FXENzZ2nkgJxcv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=7908beeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171015%2F20183456&h=5220782c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171015/20183456</a><br />\n<br />\n醉漢大鬧北⻆　木方插貨車玻璃<br />\n<br />\n9,480<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20171015/large/15la6p03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171015%2Flarge%2F15la6p03.jpg&h=4e9e892d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■醉漢情緒激動，雙手被反鎖送院。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】數名醉漢昨凌晨疑酒後失控，在北角和富道街頭肆意搗亂，先踢翻街市附近的發泡膠盒，有人更隨手拾起路邊木方，扑爛停泊路邊貨車的兩側玻璃窗及擋風玻璃，玻璃碎四濺，驚動途人報警，警員趕至拘捕其中一名涉刑事毀壞男子，他反抗時被地面玻璃碎𠝹傷，送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20171015/large/15la6p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171015%2Flarge%2F15la6p04.jpg&h=445b8034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■貨車遭木方插穿玻璃。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雙手反鎖送院<br />\n<br />\n昨凌晨零時許，數名男子途經北角和富道時，疑因飲醉酒喧鬧，又踢翻附近發泡膠盒及雜物，當行至和富道53號對開，有人更執起一條6呎長木方，向路邊一輛停泊的廢料回收貨車「施襲」，敲打貨車車窗及擋風玻璃，擊碎兩邊車窗玻璃，木方更穿過擋風玻璃插入車廂，街坊見狀報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，破壞者大多已離去，只見一名姓黃（46歲）男子留在原地，警員上前查問時，滿身酒氣的黃突發難反抗，糾纏間其手腕被地下玻璃碎𠝹傷，最終被制服拘捕，黃情緒激動雙手被反鎖送院。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎志偉  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n宜把握黃金4分鐘搶救<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n停牌男偷車藏毒衝路障"},{"pid":"54f8c782c5c40f69cf06ba219475d04b6b255d13","tid":437041,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:36:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">食屎啦LIKLN<br />\n聯合五毛投訴濕鳩塞鷗搞到佢俾人bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"}]}